{"tid":1022273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾舒祺低調簽字結婚","createTime":"2019-02-15T01:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T08:28:48.000Z","uid":130702,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"949f20aff1a540317aaea417a983786e07aabf7e","tid":1022273,"uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190215022458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190215022458&h=fdc8ac5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手鍾舒祺（Sukie）與本地樂隊Ever結他手李恒韜上月被揭入紙註冊結婚，二人趁住今日情人節正式簽字結為合法夫妻，恭喜恭喜！ <br />\n<br />\n家姐鍾舒漫見證 <br />\n<br />\nSukie晚上喺社交網晒出多張相片，宣布正式成為李太，佢留言：「14-2-2019從今以後，我們更彼此相愛，至死不渝。在牧師見證和祝福下，我們簽字結成了夫婦，今後我們的情人節將會是我們的結婚周年。」相中見到一對新人造型簡約，雙方父母都冇去，Sukie就只有邀請家姐鍾舒漫，非常低調。 <br />\n<br />\n稍後補擺婚禮 <br />\n<br />\n此外，佢亦大晒同老公喺無名指紋上嘅「婚戒」，相當幸福！佢仲表示稍後會補擺婚禮招呼親友：「朋友們，抱歉我們沒有逐一報喜信，婚禮會慢慢籌備。在將來的日子，我們李先生、李太太請各位多多指教。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190215022458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190215022458&h=ccd09b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190215022458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190215022458&h=a5d60577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190215022458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190215022458&h=7cedc978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190215022458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214231017935-0214_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190215022458&h=4df5fe0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩公婆喺無名指紋上「婚戒」！"},{"pid":"c4f518c528985cc1948c618d94ebb2fb3179325a","tid":1022273,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1df89705e7412bda358598f56ea901ecb04950ea","tid":1022273,"uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"戒指都冇錢買"},{"pid":"163115c901490ddda4724d2257acd036935f4a7c","tid":1022273,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"079f6c70207512e43ed76a1e7a45c0fc9df64317","tid":1022273,"uid":184233,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"結婚戒指都慳番<br />\n到底要有幾窮先可以諗到呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0b61cad61c95a994256cd97cd811ee608406a4","tid":1022273,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"呢隻怪物黎."},{"pid":"4839e5d4acb556752939a464ce6c3113f29966f4","tid":1022273,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"163115c901490ddda4724d2257acd036935f4a7c","tid":1022273,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c4f518c528985cc1948c618d94ebb2fb3179325a","tid":1022273,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20